name: Hypercum-4
description:
Hypercum-4 is a hypernetwork that allows user to create an NSFW image of target character getting cumshot or "bukkake" in Japanese porn terms. By default, AI seems trying to avoid from making an image of cumshot with such large amount of semen ejaculated around the character target, only covers on most areas eg. breasts and thighs but less focus on covering other areas.

This hypernetwork were trained with couple of edited anime/hentai artwork with large, thick creamy cumshot as datasets in order to make AI trying to mimicking the moment. Trained at around 5000 steps with a gradient level of 10 and trained with Berry_HD model.

Currently, this model only works with Berry_HD and Berrything_HD, requires hypernetwork strength to be set between 0.055 to 0.255. Default setting value will just make image result too horrible to see.

Additional notes: This hypernetwork also capable of forcing stable diffusion to generate artworks of mature woman without any kind of suggestive fluid in it. You can put the keyword prommpt "cum" and/or "bukkake" on negative prompt to stop SD from creating it, resulting clean artwork without heavy NSFW theme.

Warning: This model is focused solely on NSFW image generation. You must be at least 18 years old or above before using this model. I an not responsible if anything happens during the usage of this model below the legal age.
